This file explains how obtain the numerical results
described in the paper

"A lower bound for the maximum topological entropy of 4k+2-cycles"
                             by
               Lluis Alseda, David Juher and Deborah King

by using the accompanying programs. Also gives some examples of
outpout of these programs.

-----------------------------------------------------------------
To obtain the executables of the programs follow the instructions
contained in the file 'README.HowToGetThePrograms'.

CONVENTION: When we say "use the program 'xxx/yyy'" we mean:
  go to the folder 'xxx' and run the program 'yyy.exe'.
------------------------------------------------------------------

=============================================================
Table 1    Use the program 'general/CountJungreisCycles'
=======    ---------------------------------------------

Examples (period 4 and 12)
--------------------------
ajk@a01:~$ CountJungreisCycles.exe 4
Total number of Jungreis cycles 2
Total number of Jungreis cycles with zero exceptions 2

ajk@a01:~$ CountJungreisCycles.exe 12
Total number of Jungreis cycles 188892
Total number of Jungreis cycles with zero exceptions 43320

=============================================================
