==============================================================
Computation of the maximum entropy cycle in C^0_18 (Section 3)

Use the programs 'general-products/GenerateFreeAList'
                 'general-products/maxentcrossprod'
                 'general-products/maxentdotprod'
--------------------------------------------------------------
Step 1: Generate the A-list:
-------
  ajk@a01:~$ GenerateFreeAList.exe 9
  Total number of elements in the A list: 201600

NOTE: The output is a file called: free-A-list.9

Step 2: Computing alpha x beta and alpha . beta for all
------- beta lower or equal than alpha in the file free-A-list.9

     ajk@a01:~$ maxentcrossprod.exe free-A-list.9 11.0 > p18-cross.out
     ajk@a01:~$ maxentdotprod.exe free-A-list.9 11.0 > p18-dot.out

NOTES: Each of these commands last about 26 hours in the computer we
       used. So, typically it has to be run in the background:
       maxentcrossprod.exe free-A-list.9 11.0 > p18-cross.out &
       maxentdotprod.exe free-A-list.9 11.0 > p18-dot.out &

       Alternatively we can split these tasks in more jobs but
       smaller. For example the task
       ajk@a01:~$ maxentcrossprod.exe free-A-list.9 11.0 > p18-cross.out &
       could be split as:

ajk@a01:~$ maxentcrossprod.exe free-A-list.9 11.0 1:59048 > p18-cross-1:59048.out &
ajk@a01:~$ maxentcrossprod.exe free-A-list.9 11.0 59049:201600 > p18-cross-59049:201600.out &

********************************** Output *****************************************
Computing maximal entropy of products for period: 18
Listname: free-A-list.9
Alpha interval checked: ****** to *******
Filtering level 11.000000
Maximum of entropy found for the following cycles:
11.3342890140526880 (133681 . 133819)

************************************************************************************

NOTE TO THE OUTPUT: As we see, the output of maxentcrossprod and maxentdotprod
tells the spectral radius of the product permutation of the two given elements,
but alpha and beta are only specified by its position in the list.
Next we discuss how to really know some elements of the list, their product
and entropy.


==============================================================
Searching in list files

Use the programs 'general-products/ReadAList'
                 'general-products/singleprodinfo'
--------------------------------------------------------------

To really know the elements from the list that give the maximum entropy cycle
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
ajk@a01:~$ ReadAList.exe free-A-list.9 133681:133681
