NOTE: The figure has been made with the command
            'ajk@a01:~$ maxentallbounds.exe 50'
      and then the data has been manipulated with gnuplot.
      In particular it has been transformed to a logarithmic
      scale. At the end of this file you can find the gnuplot
      script to generate the figure from the output of the command
      'ajk@a01:~$ maxentallbounds.exe 50'.

      The permutations and cycles appearing in the table were known
      from the original references. The values of the entropy are
      taken from the output of 'general/maxentallbounds'.

