====================================================================
Computation of the maximum entropy cycle in C^*_22, C^*26 and C^* 30
                          (Section 6)

Use the programs 'restricted-products/GenerateRestrictedAlphaList'
                 'general-products/maxentcrossprod'
                 'general-products/maxentdotprod'
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Step 1: Generate the restricted lists.
------- To do this we have to  follow Table 5.

PERIOD 22:
ajk@a01:~$ GenerateRestrictedAlphaList.exe 11 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 10
Total number of elements in the restricted A list: 201600

NOTE: The output is a file called: restricted-A-list.11


PERIOD 26:
ajk@a01:~$ GenerateRestrictedAlphaList.exe 11 9 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 10 12
Total number of elements in the restricted A list: 201600

NOTE: The output is a file called: restricted-A-list.13


PERIOD 30:
ajk@a01:~$ GenerateRestrictedAlphaList.exe 15 13 11 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 10 12 14
Total number of elements in the restricted A list: 201600

NOTE: The output is a file called: restricted-A-list.15


Step 2: Computing the products alpha x beta and alpha . beta for all
------- beta lower or equal than alpha in the corresponding list:

ajk@a01:~$ maxentcrossprod.exe restricted-A-list.11 11.0 > p22-star.out &
ajk@a01:~$ maxentdotprod.exe restricted-A-list.13 11.0 > p26-star.out
ajk@a01:~$ maxentcrossprod.exe restricted-A-list.15 11.0 > p30-star.out &

NOTES: Each of these commands last about 26 hours in the computer we
       used.So, each task can be split exactly in the same manner
       as it was explained in the part concerning C^0_18. Also, the whole
       information about the output can be obtained with the help of the
       program 'general-products/singleprodinfo' as it has been explained
       before.

=============================================================
APPENDIX: the Gnuplot script to generate Figure 2.
=============================================================
# It is assumed that the data has been saved in the file maxentallbounds-50.dat
unset key
set terminal postscript eps
set out 'maxentallbounds-50.eps'
plot [x=4:51] "maxentallbounds-50.dat" every 2::2:::0 u 1:(log($2)-log($3)) w l,\
"maxentallbounds-50.dat" every 4::2:::0 u 1:(log($2)-log($4)) w l,\
"maxentallbounds-50.dat" every 4::4:::0 u 1:(log($2)-log($4)) w l,\
"maxentallbounds-50.dat" every 2::2:::0 u 1:(log($2)-log($3)) with points pointtype 3,\
"maxentallbounds-50.dat" every 4::2:::0 u 1:(log($2)-log($4))with points pointtype 4,\
"maxentallbounds-50.dat" every 4::4:::0 u 1:(log($2)-log($4)) with points pointtype 12
set out
quit


